::Primal Prime::

    He picked up the signal again, this time moving. Running out of the base 
and transforming to Gound Assult mode he went as fast as he could. Soon he 
could see the signal, it was Hot Rod. He really couldn't belive it.
    "Hot Rod!" Primal called out to him. But what would he say? That he 
picked up his signal for no reason, and that it was powerful? That would have 
to do. "Hot Rod, are you carring anything very powerful with you? I picked 
something up." He said pulling up under him.
